The Spring Garden is available starting at Level 25 [[Thieving]]. It is located east of the teleport spawn point.
{{Clear}}

==Lap Time==

It takes ~44 seconds to reach the sq'irk tree, yielding 81 [[spring sq'irk|spring sq'irks]] or 20 [[spring sq'irkjuice]] per hour. This assumes near perfect laps and constant running.

